text: Darko Bojanović (born 8 February 1997) is a German-born tennis player who represents Bosnia and Herzegovina. Bojanović has a career high ATP singles ranking of 937 achieved on 8 October 2018. He also has a career high ATP doubles ranking of 853 achieved on 24 September 2018. Bojanović represents Bosnia and Herzegovina at the Davis Cup, where he has a W/L record of 0–1. ==External links== * * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina male tennis players
